Sentencas: A short stack composed of two layers with anode-supported SOFCs was operated galvanostatically for 100,000 h.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: The operating temperature was 700 degrees C, the current density 0.5 A cm(-2) and humidified hydrogen and ambient air were used as gases.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: Over time, the degradation slope varied and the overall voltage degradation finally amounted to 0.5% per 1000 h. After dismantling the stack all relevant components were post-test analyzed.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: Here we report on our cell findings.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: The Ni/8YSZ support, the 8YSZ electrolyte and the perovskitic cathode contact layer appear nearly intact after 11 years.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: Most of the observed changes/interactions can be attributed to the anode (Ni/8YSZ), the barrier layer (GDC) and the cathode (LSCF).
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: Close to the barrier layer, the cathode is fragmented, elementally disintegrated and Cr poisoning was detected.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: The GDC also shows some fragmentation close to the cathode and some interaction with chromium.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: Elements from both layers, the cathode and the barrier, interdiffuse to a certain amount.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: The fuel electrode displays some foreign phase formation consisting of manganese and aluminium.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing

Sentencas: Additionally, and this was found for the first time in a solid oxide fuel cell stack, Ni enrichment in the anode was observed.
Titulo: Post-test characterization of a solid oxide fuel cell after more than 10 years of stack testing
